My Work

Projects

Blings

Blings is a ShoppingList app built with MERN Stack. ExpressJs and NodeJs was used for the backend API. ReactJs was used for the front end. Redux for managing the state. MongoDb for the datatbase.

ChatApp

Realtime instant messaging app built with Laravel and VueJs. Realtime features was implemented using Laravel echo and Pusher

Laravel-Flakes

Laravel flakes is a role based user management system, some of its features includes creating roles based on permissions, assign roles to users etc... Flakes also has a built in online payment functionality for subscribing to a blog this was implemented using Laravel Cashier and Stripe.

Satel

Simple blog with comments built with Ruby on Rails, and a basic HTTP Authentication

BraxStore

An Online store for the purchase of chocolates. Users can accumulate list of items for purchase and pay with their credit cards. BraxStore was built with Ruby on Rails and online payment using Stripe

Hegira

Hegira is a Social networking application, a Twitter motivated clone built with Ruby on Rails

MiniProject

MiniProject is a RestFul Api driven Single Page Application built with Laravel and VueJs. It also comprises of a Passwordless authentication system.
